ISLAMABAD, Feb 18 (APP): Minister for Information and Broadcasting Marriyum Aurangzeb on Saturday said interview of Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz Senior Vice President and Chief Organizer Maryam Nawaz Sharif with Saleem Safi in “Jirga programme” of Geo News will be broadcast tonight in two parts.
In a tweet, she said the first part of the interview would be telecast tonight (Saturday) at 10:05 pm and second part tomorrow (Sunday) at the same time.
